des: The Positive Community Radio plays the best in all Black Music! Breaking genre and time barriers, TPC Radio plays the best in Hip-Hop, Jazz, R&B, Blues, Gospel, Soul, Rock, Afro-Beat and so much more. From Duke Ellington to Leon Bridges... From Alice Coltrane to Esperanza Spalding.. The best of America's music in Classic Black!!! Played Exclusively at ThePositiveCommunity.com
